      <body>
         <div type="poem" xml:id="to_the_master_of_the_meteor">
            <head>TO THE MASTER OF<lb/>THE <quote>“METEOR.”</quote></head>
            
            <lg type="stanza">
               <l>LONESOME on earth's loneliest deep,</l>
               <l rend="indent">Sailor! who dost thy vigil keep—</l>
               <l>Off the Cape of Storms dost musing sweep</l>
               <l>Over monstrous waves that curl and comb;</l>
               <l>Of thee we think when here from brink</l>
               <l>We blow the mead in bubbling foam.</l>
            </lg>
            
            <lg type="stanza">
               <l>Of thee we think, in a ring we link;</l>
               <l>To the shearer of ocean's fleece we drink,</l>
               <l rend="indent">And the Meteor rolling home.</l>
            </lg>
         </div>
      </body>
